items.title: A Complete Unknown Box Office Lands On Major All-Time Domestic Chart In Just One Week
items.description: A Complete Unknown, James Mangold's Bob Dylan biopic starring Timothée Chalamet, lands on an all-time domestic box office chart after just one week.

items.title: Was Loki Ever An MCU Villain? Tom Hiddleston Didn’t Think So
items.description: Tom Hiddleston once explained why Loki was never an actual villain in the MCU, and the God of Mischief's MCU appearances support his assertion.

items.title: Nosferatu Box Office Enters Major All-Time Global Milestone For Focus Features
items.description: Nosferatu has quickly accomplished a major global box office milestone as the long-awaited horror movie remake continues to perform well.
